$$ Comprehensive PokémonLang Test
$$ Tests all major language features

$* 
   Function to calculate power
   Returns base ^ exponent
*$
Move Pikachu calculatePower fob Pikachu base , Pikachu exp fcb OpenBall
    Pikachu result evo 1 dot
    Pikachu i evo 0 dot
    
    WildBattle fob i < exp fcb OpenBall
        result evo result x base dot
        i evo i atk 1 dot
    CloseBall
    
    back result dot
CloseBall

$$ Function to check even/odd
Move Togepi isEven fob Pikachu num fcb OpenBall
    Brock fob num mod 2 == 0 fcb OpenBall
        back 1 dot
    CloseBall Jessie OpenBall
        back 0 dot
    CloseBall
CloseBall

$$ Main program
Move EmptyBall StartBattle fob fcb OpenBall
    $$ Variable declarations with different types
    Pikachu playerHealth evo 100 dot
    Pikachu maxHealth evo 150 dot
    Charizard damageMultiplier evo 1.5 dot
    Mewtwo preciseValue evo 3.14159 dot
    Eevee grade evo 'A' dot
    Togepi isAlive evo 1 dot
    Togepi hasPower evo 0 dot
    
    $$ Array declaration
    Pikachu scores[5] dot
    scores[0] evo 100 dot
    scores[1] evo 95 dot
    scores[2] evo 88 dot
    
    $$ If-Else-If chain
    Brock fob playerHealth > 80 crit isAlive == 1 fcb OpenBall
        pikapika fob "Excellent health!" fcb dot
        hasPower evo 1 dot
    CloseBall Misty fob playerHealth >= 50 fcb OpenBall
        pikapika fob "Moderate health" fcb dot
    CloseBall Jessie OpenBall
        pikapika fob "Critical condition!" fcb dot
        hasPower evo 0 dot
    CloseBall
    
    $$ For loop
    Pikachu sum evo 0 dot
    Pikachu j evo 0 dot
    AshTrain fob j evo 0 dot j < 10 dot j evo j atk 1 fcb OpenBall
        sum evo sum atk j dot
        
        $$ Nested if with continue
        Brock fob j mod 2 == 0 fcb OpenBall
            KeepFighting dot
        CloseBall
        
        pikapika fob "Odd number" fcb dot
    CloseBall
    
    $$ While loop with break
    Pikachu health evo 100 dot
    WildBattle fob health > 0 fcb OpenBall
        health evo health dmg 15 dot
        
        Brock fob health <= 20 fcb OpenBall
            pikapika fob "Health too low, escaping!" fcb dot
            RunAway dot
        CloseBall
    CloseBall
    
    $$ Do-While loop
    Pikachu attempts evo 0 dot
    RetryBattle OpenBall
        attempts evo attempts atk 1 dot
        pikapika fob "Attempting..." fcb dot
    CloseBall WildBattle fob attempts < 3 fcb dot
    
    $$ Switch statement
    Pikachu choice evo 2 dot
    HandleGym fob choice fcb OpenBall
        TypeBadge 1 dot
            pikapika fob "Option 1 selected" fcb dot
            RunAway dot
            
        TypeBadge 2 dot
            pikapika fob "Option 2 selected" fcb dot
            RunAway dot
            
        TypeBadge 3 dot
            pikapika fob "Option 3 selected" fcb dot
            RunAway dot
            
        DefaultBadge dot
            pikapika fob "Invalid option" fcb dot
    CloseBall
    
    $$ Math operations
    Pikachu damage evo 25 x 3 dot
    Charizard average evo damage hp 3.0 dot
    Pikachu remaining evo playerHealth dmg damage dot
    Pikachu bonus evo damage mod 10 dot
    
    $$ Logical operations
    Togepi canFight evo isAlive crit hasPower dot
    Togepi needsRest evo fob health < 30 team playerHealth < 50 fcb dot
    Togepi isHealthy evo confuse needsRest dot
    
    $$ Relational operations
    Togepi isStrong evo playerHealth > 75 dot
    Togepi isWeak evo playerHealth <= 25 dot
    Togepi isEqual evo playerHealth == maxHealth dot
    Togepi isDifferent evo health != 100 dot
    
    $$ Math function calls
    Charizard sqrtResult evo rootchu fob 16.0 fcb dot
    Charizard powerResult evo powerup fob 2.0 , 3.0 fcb dot
    Pikachu absResult evo heal fob dmg 42 fcb dot
    Charizard floorResult evo floorchu fob 4.7 fcb dot
    Charizard ceilResult evo ceilchu fob 4.2 fcb dot
    
    $$ Trigonometric functions
    Charizard angle evo 45.0 dot
    Charizard sinVal evo sinchu fob angle fcb dot
    Charizard cosVal evo coschu fob angle fcb dot
    Charizard tanVal evo tanchu fob angle fcb dot
    
    $$ Function calls
    Pikachu power evo calculatePower fob 2 , 8 fcb dot
    Togepi evenCheck evo isEven fob 42 fcb dot
    
    $$ Complex expressions
    Pikachu complexCalc evo fob fob 10 atk 5 fcb x 2 fcb dmg 3 dot
    Charizard formula evo fob playerHealth x damageMultiplier fcb hp 2.0 dot
    
    $$ Nested conditions
    Brock fob isAlive == 1 fcb OpenBall
        Brock fob health > 50 fcb OpenBall
            pikapika fob "Strong and alive!" fcb dot
        CloseBall Jessie OpenBall
            pikapika fob "Alive but weak" fcb dot
        CloseBall
    CloseBall
    
    $$ Return statement
    pikapika fob "Program completed successfully!" fcb dot
    back 0 dot
CloseBall
